Invocation Name: my aquarium
des:
Aquarium Screensaver HD on your Echo Show or Echo Spot device (required a screen). Aquarium plays a relaxing aquarium on your Echo Show or Echo Spot. Great fun for your living room, kitchen or bedroom! 

+ Ask "Alexa, open My Aquarium" to open skill. Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
